    <stitle>SINGLE REDUCTION, TANDEM AXLE: INTERNATIONAL - LUBRICATION - OPTIONAL LUBE FILTER</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>OPTIONAL LUBE FILTER</title>
        <para>Spicer recommends the lube filter be replaced annually or at 100,000 miles (160,000 kilometers) whichever
            comes first. Use International filter number 1665311C1.
        </para>
        <para>Remove magnetic screen for inspection and cleaning. Temporarily insert a 3/4" NPT plug in the magnetic
            screen hole to prevent excessive loss of lube during this operation.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
